{{Politics of the Isle of Man}}
The '''Chief Secretary''' ({{Lang-gv|Ard-scrudeyr}}) is the head of the [[Isle of Man]] [[Civil Service]]. The current Chief Secretary is Will Greenhow.
The Chief Secretary is responsible for the function of the '''Chief Secretary's Office''' ({{Lang-gv|Oik yn Ard-scrudeyr}}) and provides advice and guidance to the [[Chief Minister of the Isle of Man|Chief Minister]] and the [[Council of Ministers of the Isle of Man|Council of Ministers]].
